DRUGS

Usage: ^gUSE <drug>^n

Drugs have a variety of effects, depending on the type of drug you 
are using. They often have beneficial affects on the high (Including
stat bonuses, initiative bonuses, pain resistance, etc) but you will 
suffer penalties as you come down. Overuse of drugs can also result 
in addiction. 

Addiction can be very damaging to your health. If you continue with
using the drugs it can result in Body loss, condition loss, and
eventually permanent death if taking to the extreme.
